{"word":"H1494 - גַּזָז - gazâz - gaw-zaz' - Cut off","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גַּזָז</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>gazâz"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>gaw-zaz'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Cut off"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மயிர்க்கத்தரி, சிரை, அறுப்புண்டு போ"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to shear, to mow"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to shear"},{"paragraph":"2) a shearer (participle)"},{"paragraph":"b) (Niphal) to be cut off, to be destroyed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root (akin to <a href=\"#/H1468 - גּוּז - gûwz - gooz/1468\">H1468</a>); to <i>cut</i> off; specifically to <i>shear</i> a flock, or <i>shave</i> the hair; figuratively to <i>destroy</i> an enemy: - cut off (down), poll, shave, ([sheep-]) shear (-er)."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1488 - גֵּז - gêz - gaze/1488\">H1488</a>, <a href=\"#/H1492 - גָּזַּה - gâzzah - gaz-zaw'/1492\">H1492</a>, <a href=\"#/H1494 - גַּזָז - gazâz - gaw-zaz'/1494\">H1494</a>, <a href=\"#/H1495 - גָּזֵז - Gâzêz - gaw-zaze'/1495\">H1495</a>"}]}